17 — Grading-friendly checklist (for teacher expectations)

Authentication & registration flow implemented

Course catalog with filtering & search

Course detail and enrollment flow

Lesson viewer with progress tracking

Assignment submission (with file upload simulation)

Quiz with auto-grading (MCQs)

Student & teacher dashboards with at least 3 widgets each

Responsive design + basic accessibility checks

Clean code structure + README


Mark each feature as: ✔️ Done / ⚠️ Partial / ❌ Not done for the teacher.


